cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP (127.0.0.4) will prevent F1 interface connectivity between CU and DU, causing setup failures and configuration rejection.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Modifying the local N address to an unreachable IP (127.0.0.4) will disrupt F1 communication and routing, leading to connectivity issues with the CU and system faults.
